    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-oriented example featuring the high-revving S54B32 inline-six engine. The powertrain remains robust, with a recently overhauled VANOS system and a cooling system refreshed with an aluminum radiator to mitigate heat soak. Power is delivered through a Getrag 420G six-speed manual transmission and a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential, ensuring exceptional mechanical traction. The chassis has been addressed for common platform fatigue with a reinforced rear subframe and upgraded bushings. While the exterior displays minor road-rash and honest patina consistent with its mileage, the suspension geometry is dialed in, and the engine maintains strong compression across all cylinders. This is a mechanically sorted machine ready for the apex.",
